Samsung Digital Health - Health Data API Reference 1.0.0

This document describes APIs for the com.samsung.android.sdk.healthdata of Samsung Digital Health SDK.

See: Description

Packages 
Package Description
com.samsung.android.sdk.healthdata
This package provides classes and interfaces for the Data Framework of Samsung Digital Health.
This document describes APIs for the com.samsung.android.sdk.healthdata of Samsung Digital Health SDK.
The packages above contain classes and interfaces which enable you to create applications with the following functionalities.

  • Health data store
  • Health data type
  • Privacy

For more information related to the development environment, fundamentals, use cases, and sample descriptions, see Programming Guide in the SamsungDigitalHealthSdk/HealthData/Docs folder.
